17.3	In view of the foregoing observations, we have recommended that management:
Justify the noted lapses and henceforth, management familiarized themselves with the relevant provisions with regards to the utilization of the LDRRM Funds;
Push for the enactment of a local ordinance creating the Disaster Risk Reduction and Management (DRRM) Office including the required staffing/personnel. Upon enactment consider the immediate hiring of qualified DRRM Officer and staff;
